sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SW as Session Sweeper
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant FIN as Session Finalizer
    participant LLM as Model ekstraksi
    participant KG as Neo4j
    participant VEC as pgvector

    SW->>PG: Cari sesi idle
    PG-->>SW: Daftar sesi layak finalisasi
    SW->>FIN: Finalisasi sesi
    FIN->>PG: Ambil riwayat pesan
    FIN->>LLM: Ekstraksi memori penting
    LLM-->>FIN: Entitas dan relasi
    FIN->>KG: Tulis node dan relasi
    FIN->>VEC: Simpan embedding memori
    FIN->>PG: Tandai sesi selesai diproses
